      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;games&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Games&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#games&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;bogwalker&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Bogwalker&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#bogwalker&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../bogwalker.gif&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Logic puzzle game. It&amp;rsquo;s like Minesweeper, but you can sense the mines from further away. I made this in 2 weeks. It&amp;rsquo;s finished but I will refactor it at some point.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://nikola-stefanov.itch.io/bogwalker&#34;&gt;itch&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/nik1oo/bogwalker&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;blade--eye&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Blade &amp;amp; Eye&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#blade--eye&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../blade-and-eye.gif&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;First-person golf-themed fantasy adventure game I made for a game jam. It&amp;rsquo;s still very early in development, but you can play the demo on Itch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
