      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;other&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Other&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#other&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;game-boy-advance-emulator&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Game Boy Advance Emulator&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#game-boy-advance-emulator&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Phase-level GBA emulator, employing Test-driven development. Still in pre-alpha stage. I&amp;rsquo;ve implemented the ARMv4T ISA and I&amp;rsquo;ve executed the BIOS.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/nik1oo/gbana&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;sdf-graphics-engine&#34;&gt;&#xA;  SDF Graphics Engine&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sdf-graphics-engine&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../wiggler.gif&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is a skeletal animation demo in my SDF graphics engine. The scene is composed by combining offline- and online-rendered images and then post-processing effects on top of that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
